<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{قُلْ هُوَ اللهُ أَحَدٌ , اللهُ الصَّمَدُ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٨٠:</span> يُقَالُ: لَا يُنَوَّنُ <span class="c3">{أَحَدٌ}</span> أَيْ: وَاحِدٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
